// Peacetime Remastered - ALL declarative content in one file (the amd_doc table-of-contents
// model). Loaded once by peacetime_remastered.mast with the combined mission vocabulary:
//   PR_DOC = document_get_amd_file(get_mission_dir_filename("maps/peacetime_remastered.amd"),
//                                  data_parser=amd_mission_data)
// then each section is handed to its own loader:
//   quest_grant_amd(SHARED, amd_section(PR_DOC, "florbin_case"))   // the Florbin quest tree
//   for p in players: quest_grant_amd(p.id, amd_section(PR_DOC, "jobs"))
//   science_define_scan_amd(amd_section(PR_DOC, "scans"))
//   landmarks_spawn(amd_section(PR_DOC, "landmarks"))
// The cargo-ship scans (## Cargo Scans, suspect/discovered) also live here so the remaster
// owns them; peacetime.mast registers that section for BOTH maps during the transition (the
// original still runs the same kidnap_caper). LM's global sides stay in their own file.

# [Peacetime Remastered](peacetime_remastered)

// ---- The Florbin case: a shared quest tree (nested steps -> florbin/brief .. florbin/alive).
// florbin_quest_watch bridges the reused kidnap_caper kidnap_status flag to these signals.
## [Florbin Case](florbin_case)

### [The Florbin Affair](florbin)
---
Scope: shared
State: active
---
Ambassador Florbin has been kidnapped and smuggled out in a cargo container. Follow the cargo trail, find him, and bring him home to DS 1 - alive.

#### [Take the Case](brief)
---
Scope: shared
State: active
When: signal case_opened
Then: reveal florbin/trail
---
Contact DS 1 to open the investigation.

#### [Identify the Kidnapper](trail)
---
Scope: shared
State: secret
When: signal suspect_identified
Then: reveal florbin/subdue
---
Follow the cargo trail: interview stations and bio-scan suspect holds to find which ship is hiding the ambassador.

#### [Subdue the Kidnapper](subdue)
---
Scope: shared
State: secret
When: signal kidnapper_subdued
Then: reveal florbin/recover
---
Do NOT destroy the ship - the ambassador is aboard. Drop its shields below 50% (or use a secret codecase) to force its surrender.

#### [Recover and Return Florbin](recover)
---
Scope: shared
State: secret
When: signal florbin_delivered
---
Collect the escape pod and dock it at DS 1.

#### [Keep Florbin Alive](alive)
---
Scope: shared
State: active
Fail on signal: florbin_killed
---
The case is lost if the ship carrying the ambassador is destroyed before he escapes.

// ---- The peacetime job board. Granted PER PLAYER SHIP so credit rewards pay to the side.
// Signals come from the mission's MAST plumbing (//damage/destroy, comms, pr_mercy_watch).
// Counts here are the targets; pr_jobs_setup spawns matching objects - keep in sync.
## [Jobs](jobs)

### [Gunnery Qualification](job_gunnery)
---
State: idle
Goal: signal 5 drone_down
Pays: 200 credits
---
Weapons drill: destroy all the target drones.

### [Rock Breakers](job_rocks)
---
State: idle
Goal: signal 4 rock_cleared
Pays: 150 credits
---
Clear the hazard asteroids from the shipping lane.

### [Board the Poacher](job_poacher)
---
State: idle
Goal: signal poacher_boarded
Fail on signal: poacher_killed
Pays: 300 credits
---
Disable the unregistered trawler (drop its shields below 50%) and demand its surrender. Do NOT destroy it.

### [Mercy Run](job_mercy)
---
State: idle
Goal: signal mercy_reached
Fail after: 6 minutes
Pays: 250 credits
---
A shuttle is adrift and losing life support. Reach it before the clock runs out.

### [Customs Patrol](job_customs)
---
State: idle
Goal: signal 4 customs_cleared
Pays: 120 credits
---
Hail and clear the civilian traders for transit.

### [Anomaly Survey](job_survey)
---
State: idle
Goal: scan 3 anomaly
Reveals: Survey logged: a stable subspace distortion. No threat - filed with the science log.
Pays: 130 credits
---
Have Science scan the sensor anomalies and log them.

